summary:
I have a lot of experience translating texts from English to Dutch and from Dutch to English. I am specialized in translating scientific texts on psychology, theology and development aid. I have also translated a great number of brochures and booklets on marketing and pr and ICT-related texts.

Specialties: Psychology, astrology, theology and development aid
